<p>Donated by Mildred Lyons, widow of John Lyons, in 1957. The collection was transferred to New York University with the rest of the manuscript collections in the Tamiment Institute Library in 1963. The accession number 1963.004 is associated with this collection.</p>  </acqinfo>
